          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Photoreaction mechanisms of Li-6 were  studied  using",
                " bremsstrahlung  below the (gamma,H-3) threshold.  It",
                " was confirmed by the  present  work  that  only  the",
                " Li-6(gamma,p)He-5  and  Li-6(gamma,n)Li-5  reactions",
                " actually occur  in  the  energy  range  of  incident",
                " gamma-ray lower than the (gamma,t) threshold,and the",
                " Li-6(gamma,n+p)He-4 reaction in various  types  does",
                " not  occur  in  practice  although  this reaction is",
                " energetically  possible.  The  assignment   of   the",
                " reactions Li-6(gamma,p)He-5 and Li-6(gamma,n)Li-5 to",
                " the  measured  photoproton  spectrum  for  15.4  MeV",
                " irradiation is presented."
              ]
            }
          ],
